             "Description": "The contractor shall apply the procedures from the ESA Security Directives for the accessing, handling and storage of information. These procedures ensures the protection of information from improper use or unauthorised divulgation.",\n                "MEHARI_W": "3",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"8d588fca-262f-4ea3-8e1a-80c12c87ea7b\\":\\"ISO-27001:2005\\",\\"1ee11caa-a0e5-41d8-8df7-7364ab904aa9\\":\\"ESA\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"8d588fca-262f-4ea3-8e1a-80c12c87ea7b\\":\\"A.10.7.3\\",\\"1ee11caa-a0e5-41d8-8df7-7364ab904aa9\\":\\"Contract\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "For HSO-G, the [applicable Secops Procedure] also apply."\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0099",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Backup audits on separate physical systems",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "The system shall backup audit records onto a physically different system or system component than the system or component being audited.",\n                "MEHARI_W": "3",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"1288c548-6b4a-4f04-b067-464e00a9509d\\":\\"NIST-SP800-53_rev4\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"1288c548-6b4a-4f04-b067-464e00a9509d\\":\\"AU-9(2)\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "This helps to ensure that a compromise of the information system being audited does not also result in a compromise of the audit records."\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0276",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n        