	(4, '1', 'Are dedicated managers  (computer and telecom security, general security in the workplace (documents, fax, telephone), general physical security of the sites and premises) or a designated point of contact (HR for awareness and training, work contracts, user account and access rights management, responsibility for disciplining malicious acts or internal negligence) assigned to all areas of security?', 'QUESTION', '01A01-01', '01A01', '4', '2', '', 'E1', '', '', NULL),
