	(12, '3', 'Have the structure and organization of the management of information systems security been defined in detail: CISO, local responsibilities and contacts, roles and responsibilities towards operational managers and is this organizational structure in operation?', 'QUESTION', '01A02-03', '01A02', '4', '2', '3', 'E2', '6.1.1', '6.1.2', NULL),
