	(14, '5', 'Have the mode of managing security and the decision processes been defined in detail: methodology used (for audit of exposure, risk analysis etc.), associated tools, actors (organization, support, training, expertise, advice etc.)?', 'QUESTION', '01A02-05', '01A02', '4', '', '', 'E2', '6.1.1', '6.1.2', NULL),
