 "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "05A04-04",\n              "index": "4",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "For each serious incident on the local area network, have an expected resolution time and escalation procedure been determined in the case of failure or delay of the anticipated corrective actions?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "05A04-05",\n              "index": "5",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Are the diagnostic, management and reconfiguration tools of the local area network protected against all possible untimely or malicious action?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "3",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "05A04-06",\n              "index": "6",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Do incident recovery plans and procedures cover the eventual loss of data (especially loss of requests and messages)?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "05A04-07",\n              "index": "7",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Are diagnostic and reconfiguration means regularly audited in order to assure a satisfactory minimum functioning of the local area network in the case of an incident?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "3",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            }\n          ],\n          "gasf": [\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0102",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Management of the software internal operations",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "Internal controls shall be implemented to identify any processing issues and malicious deliberate acts. Such controls should be settled to avoid any potential frauds.",\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"018a863a-9ae3-458e-a6e3-b40e8e490ee0\\":\\"ISO-27001:2005\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"018a863a-9ae3-458e-a6e3-b40e8e490ee0\\":\\"A.12.2.2\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V