wers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "12.4.1; 16.1.5",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A12\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Operations security\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A12.4\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Logging and monitoring\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"12.4.1\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Event logging\\"},{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A16\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Information security incident management\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A16.1\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Management of information security incidents and improvements\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"16.1.5\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Response to information security incidents\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": "10.10.5"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "05D03-06",\n              "index": "6",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Does this system incorporate a categorization of incidents including statistics and dashboards generation destined for use by the Information Security Officer?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "; 16.1.5",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A16\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Information security incident management\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A16.1\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Management of information security incidents and improvements\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"16.1.5\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Response to information security incidents\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "05D03-07",\n              "index": "7",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is the incident management system strictly controlled with regard to unauthorized or illicit modification?\\r\\nA strict control requires a reinforced protection in order to modify records and an audit trail or protection by digitally signing all modifications of records.",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "3",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "05D03-08",\n              "index": "8",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is each major incident on the network subject to a specific follow-up (nature and description, priority, technical solution, analysis in progress, expected resolution lead time etc.)?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "16.1.1",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A16\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Information security incident management\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A16.1\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Management of information security incidents and improvements\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"16.1.1\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Responsibilities and procedures\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": "13.2.1"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n 