	(901, '6', 'MEHARI_NetworkOperations', 'QUESTIONNAIRE', '06', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '{\n  "category": "06",\n  "index": "6",\n  "type": "MEHARI_NetworkOperations",\n  "questions": [\n    {\n      "category": "06A",\n      "index": "6",\n      "type": "CATEGORY",\n      "value": "Security of operations procedures ",\n      "children": [\n        {\n          "category": "06A01",\n          "index": "1",\n          "type": "CATEGORY",\n          "value": "Security in the relationship with operational personnel (employees, suppliers or service providers)",\n          "children": [\n            {\n              "category": "06A01-01",\n              "index": "1",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is there a security policy specifically aimed at operational network personnel covering all the aspects of information security (confidentiality of information, service and information availability, integrity of information and configurations, trace ability, etc. )?  ",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "1",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "06A01-02",\n              "index": "2",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is operational network personnel required to sign contract clauses of adherence to that security policy (no matter their status: permanent or temporary staff, students, etc.)?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "06A01-03",\n              "index": "3",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Do these clauses make clear that the obligation to respect security applies to all information no matter what the medium is (paper, magnetic, optical, etc.)?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "2",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "06A01-04",\n              "index": "4",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Do these clauses make clear, if necessary and legally possible, that the obligation to respect the security policy applies without limitation in time? \\r\\nThis applies, in particular, to the clauses concerning confidentiality, they may (and often must) continue after the end of the contract linking (directly or indirectly) the employee or  service provider or partner to the company",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "2",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "06A01-05",\n              "index": "5",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Do these clauses make clear that the personnel has an obligation not to tolerate any action contrary to security from other people?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "3",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "06A01-06",\n              "index": "6",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Does the signature of these clauses represent a formal commitment?\\r\\nIn order to achieve a formal commitment, the personnel should explicitly state that his/her signature implies having understood and accepted the security policy",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "3",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "06A01-07",\n              "index": "7",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Are these same clauses obligatory for contractors working on network operations?\\r\\nPractically, the contractors should ensure that their personnel sign individually and explicitly under the same conditions than internal staff.",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "2",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "06A01-08",\n              "index": "8",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is there a mandatory and well adapted training course aimed at network operations personnel?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "06A01-09",\n              "index": "9",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Are the confidentiality agreements, signed by personnel, securely kept (at least in a locked cupboard )?  ",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "3",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "06A01-10",\n              "index": "10",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Are the confidentiality agreements, signed by external contractors, securely kept (at least in a locked cupboard )?  ",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "3",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "06A01-11",\n              "index": "11",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is there a regular audit, at least once a year, of the effective application of the signature procedure by  operational personnel (directly employed by the company or indirectly through a service company)?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "3",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            }\n          ],\n          "gasf": [\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0143",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Deny network traffic by default / allow by exception",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "The system shall, at managed interfaces, d