tication parameters, control of routing tables etc.) detailed and kept up to date and are they reviewed before any start of production of a new version?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "14.2.9",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A14\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"System acquisition, development and maintenance\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A14.2\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Security in development and support processes\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"14.2.9\\",\\"Control\\":\\"System acceptance testing\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": "11.4.4; 10.3.2"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "06A02-10",\n              "index": "10",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Are the security parameters and configuration rules controlled before any new version is installed and operated? ",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "14.2.9",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A14\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"System acquisition, development and maintenance\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A14.2\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Security in development and support processes\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"14.2.9\\",\\"Control\\":\\"System acceptance testing\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": "11.4.4; 10.3.2"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "06A02-11",\n              "index": "11",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is it considered the possible impact over the continuity plans due the system changes?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "14.2.9",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A14\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"System acquisition, development and maintenance\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A14.2\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Security in development and support processes\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"14.2.9\\",\\"Control\\":\\"System acceptance testing\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": "10.3.2"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "06A02-12",\n              "index": "12",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Are any exemptions from the prior risk analysis and control of security parameters subject to strict procedures requiring the signature of a senior manager?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "06A02-13",\n              "index": "13",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is the start of production of new equipment or software only possible by operational staff?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "12.5.1",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A12\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Operations security\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A12.5\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Control of operational software\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"12.5.1\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Installation of software on operational systems\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "2",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": "12.4.1; 6.1.4"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "06A02-14",\n              "index": "14",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is the start of production of new equipment or software only possible following a defined validation and authorization process?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "12.5.1",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A12\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Operations security\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A12.5\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Control of operational software\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"12.5.1\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Installation of software on operational systems\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "3",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": "12.4.1; 6.1.4"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "06A02-15",\n              "index": "15",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Are all the control procedures related to start of production subject to regular audit?",\n              "children": []