shall only allow incoming communications from authorised sources routed to authorised destinations.",\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"da224a4c-22c7-4d94-8f91-0d19bb5cd0fe\\":\\"NIST-SP800-53_rev4\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"da224a4c-22c7-4d94-8f91-0d19bb5cd0fe\\":\\"SC-7(11)\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "This provides determinations that source and destination address pairs represent authorised/allowed communications. Such determinations can be based on several factors including, for example, the presence of source/destination address pairs in lists of authorised/allowed communications, the absence of address pairs in lists of unauthorised/disallowed pairs, or meeting more general rules for authorised/allowed source/destination pairs."\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0268",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Synchronise internal clocks",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "The system shall synchronise its internal clock with the [authoritative time source] every [update frequency].",\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"057ea763-6b84-43dd-abf0-c4d9dbb575b9\\":\\"NIST-SP800-53_rev4\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"057ea763-6b84-43dd-abf0-c4d9dbb575b9\\":\\"AU-8(1)\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "This provides uniformity of time stamps for information systems with multiple system clocks and systems connected over a network."\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0251",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Isolate processing threads",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "The system shall maintain a separate execution domain for each thread when multi-threaded processing is used.",\n                "MEHARI_W": "3",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"bd96bdab-df03-4d98-b170-69197a4a00aa\\":\\"NIST-SP800-53_rev4\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"bd96bdab-df03-4d98-b170-69197a4a00aa\\":\\"SC-39(2)\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "-"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0031",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Disable default accounts",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "The contractor shall include the deactivation of default accounts in the user account management documentation in the [host document].",\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"2026547a-1547-4627-9ad2-214bd95d4179\\":\\"INDAS0607F074.1_TN2_SRS\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"2026547a-1547-4627-9ad2-214bd95d4179\\":\\"TCA_IDENT_0030\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "Default or standard accounts / account names (e.g. Guest) shall be disabled.\\nThese accounts are an easy target even for not-too-experienced attackers."\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            }\n          ],\n          "answers": {\n            "MEHARI_W": "",\n            "MEHARI_Min": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n            "MEHARI_Max": "",\n  