       {\n              "category": "08B03-05",\n              "index": "5",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is a check made of the proof of origin and integrity of received maintenance module or a new version, from the editor or the manufacturer (for operating systems)?  ",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "08B03-06",\n              "index": "6",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Are the signing and signing control tools protected against any unauthorized usage?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "08B03-07",\n              "index": "7",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Does the inhibition of the automatic control of seals trigger an alarm to a manager?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n 