	(1137, '8', 'Security of operational procedures ', 'CATEGORY', '08A', '08', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1138, '1', 'Consideration of security in relation with operational personnel (permanent and temporary staff)', 'CATEGORY', '08A01', '08A', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1139, '1', 'Is there a security policy, specifically aimed at operations personnel, related to information systems?\r\nThis policy should cover the requirements for the protection of information as well as the protection of physical assets and processes and mention the forbidden behaviors', 'QUESTION', '08A01-01', '08A01', '4', '', '', 'E1', '11.2.1', '9.2.1', NULL),
	(1140, '2', 'Is information systems operations personnel required to sign contract clauses of adherence to that security policy (no matter their status: permanent or temporary staff, students, etc.)?', 'QUESTION', '08A01-02', '08A01', '4', '', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(1141, '3', 'Do these clauses make clear that the obligation to respect that security policy applies to information at large (whichever the support : paper, magnetic, optical, etc.)?', 'QUESTION', '08A01-03', '08A01', '2', '2', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(1142, '4', 'Do these clauses make clear, if necessary and legally possible, that the obligation to respect the security policy applies without limitation in time?\r\nThis applies, in particular, to the clauses concerning confidentiality, they may (and often must) continue after the end of the contract linking (directly or indirectly) the employee or  service provider or partner to the company', 'QUESTION', '08A01-04', '08A01', '4', '2', '', 'E3', '', '', NULL),
	(1143, '5', 'Do these clauses make clear that the personnel has an obligation not to tolerate any action contrary to security from other people?', 'QUESTION', '08A01-05', '08A01', '4', '3', '', 'E3', '', '', NULL),
	(1144, '6', 'Does the signature of these clauses represent a formal commitment?\r\nIn order to achieve a formal commitment, the personnel should explicitly state that his/her signature implies having understood and accepted the security policy', 'QUESTION', '08A01-06', '08A01', '4', '3', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(1145, '7', 'Are these same clauses obligatory for contractors working on systems operations?\r\nPractically, the contractors should ensure that their personnel sign individually and explicitly under the same conditions than internal staff. ', 'QUESTION', '08A01-07', '08A01', '4', '2', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(1146, '8', 'Is there a mandatory and well adapted training course aimed at systems operation personnel?', 'QUESTION', '08A01-08', '08A01', '2', '', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(1147, '9', 'Are the security policy compliance agreements, signed by personnel, securely kept (at least in a locked cupboard )?  ', 'QUESTION', '08A01-09', '08A01', '2', '3', '', 'R1', '', '', NULL),
	(1148, '10', 'Are the security policy compliance agreements, signed by external contractors, securely kept (at least in a locked cupboard )?  ', 'QUESTION', '08A01-10', '08A01', '2', '3', '', 'R1', '', '', NULL),
	(1149, '11', 'Is there a regular audit, at least once a year, of the effective application of the signature procedure by  operational personnel (directly employed by the company or indirectly through a service company) ?  ', 'QUESTION', '08A01-11', '08A01', '2', '3', '', 'C1', '', '', NULL),
	(1150, '2', 'Control of the operational tools and utilities', 'CATEGORY', '08A02', '08A', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1151, '1', 'Have different profiles been defined for the systems operation staff (administration and management of configurations, administration of security equipment, monitoring, audit and investigation)? ', 'QUESTION', '08A02-01', '08A02', '4', '', '', 'E1', '12.6.2', '', NULL),
	(1152, '2', 'Are all members of systems operation staff attributed with one of these profiles? ', 'QUESTION', '08A02-02', '08A02', '4', '', '', 'E2', '12.6.2', '', NULL),
	(1153, '3', 'Have all the sensitive system tools and utilities (rights administration, configuration management, backups, copies, hot restarts, etc.) been exhaustively audited and listed for each profile?', 'QUESTION', '08A02-03', '08A02', '4', '', '', 'E2', ' 9.4.4; 12.6.2', '11.5.4', NULL),
	(1154, '4', 'Is it possible only for holders of a certain profile to use the corresponding tools and utilities subsequent to proper strong authentication (smart card or token card)?', 'QUESTION', '08A02-04', '08A02', '2', '2', '', 'E3', ' 9.4.4; 12.6.2', '11.5.4', NULL),
