	(1437, '4', 'Does this system centralize incidents detected both by operational personnel and by users?', 'QUESTION', '08E03-04', '08E03', '4', '2', '', 'E2', '16.1.5', '', NULL),
	(1438, '5', 'Does the system cater for a systematic follow-up of necessary actions?', 'QUESTION', '08E03-05', '08E03', '4', '', '', 'E3', '16.1.5', '', NULL),
	(1439, '6', 'Does this system incorporate a categorization of incidents with statistics generation and dashboards destined for use by the Information Security Officer?', 'QUESTION', '08E03-06', '08E03', '4', '', '', 'E3', '16.1.5', '', NULL),
	(1440, '7', 'Is the incident management system strictly controlled with regard to unauthorized or inadvertent modification?\r\nA strict control requires a reinforced protection in order to modify records and an audit trail of all modifications of records or protection by electronic seal on all records modification.', 'QUESTION', '08E03-07', '08E03', '4', '3', '', 'R1', '', '', NULL),
	(1441, '8', 'Is each major incident on systems or applications subject to a specific follow-up (nature and description, priority, technical solution, progress analysis, expected resolution lead time etc.)?', 'QUESTION', '08E03-08', '08E03', '4', '', '', 'E2', '16.1.1', '', NULL),
	(1442, '8', ' Control of administrative rights', 'CATEGORY', '08F', '08', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1443, '1', 'Control of administrative access rights granted on systems', 'CATEGORY', '08F01', '08F', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1444, '1', 'Have profiles been defined, within IT operations staff, corresponding to each type of activity (system administration, administration of security equipment, system monitoring, management of data storage and backup functions etc.)?', 'QUESTION', '08F01-01', '08F01', '1', '', '', 'E1', '6.1.2; 9.2.3; 9.2.5', '10.1.3; 11.2.2', NULL),
	(1445, '2', 'For each profile have the necessary rights and privileges been defined? ', 'QUESTION', '08F01-02', '08F01', '4', '2', '', 'E1', '6.1.2', '10.1.3', NULL),
	(1446, '3', 'Does the process of attributing special rights require the formal authorization of management (or the manager responsible for external service providers) at a sufficiently high level?', 'QUESTION', '08F01-03', '08F01', '4', '2', '', 'E2', '6.1.2', '10.1.3', NULL),
	(1447, '4', 'Is the process of attributing special rights allocated only in relation to the profile of the holder?', 'QUESTION', '08F01-04', '08F01', '4', '2', '', 'E2', '6.1.2', '10.1.3', NULL),
	(1448, '5', 'Is the process of granting (modification or revocation) of special rights to an individual strictly controlled?\r\nA strict control requires a formal recognition of the signature (electronic or not) of the requestor, that there be a tight control of access in order to attribute or modify such rights and that any modification of special rights be logged and audited.', 'QUESTION', '08F01-05', '08F01', '4', '2', '3', 'R1', '9.2.3; 9.2.5', '11.2.2', NULL),
	(1449, '6', 'Is there a systematic process of removal of special rights at the time of departure or role change of IT operations staff?', 'QUESTION', '08F01-06', '08F01', '2', '', '', 'E2', '9.2.5', '11.2.4', NULL),
	(1450, '7', 'Is there a regular audit, at least once a year, of all special rights attributed ?', 'QUESTION', '08F01-07', '08F01', '1', '2', '', 'C1', '9.2.5', '11.2.4', NULL),
	(1451, '2', 'Authentication of administrators and operational personnel  ', 'CATEGORY', '08F02', '08F', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1452, '1', 'Is the authentication protocol used for administrators or holders of special rights considered to be secure?\r\nAn authentication protocol is considered secure if it is not susceptible to being broken by a listening device on the network or rendered inoperable by specialists tools (in particular password crack tools ). Such security usually uses cryptographic methods.', 'QUESTION', '08F02-01', '08F02', '4', '', '4', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(1453, '2', 'Are the rules, for instance in the case of passwords, considered to be very strict?\r\nStrict rules impose the use of tested non-trivial passwords, using a mixture of different types of characters and of a reasonable length (ten characters). It is desirable that these rules have been approved by the Information Security Officer', 'QUESTION', '08F02-02', '08F02', '2', '', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(1454, '3', 'Is there a consistent control of the administrator`s rights, of its context, and of the suitability of this context with the requested access, as per formal rules of access control?', 'QUESTION', '08F02-03', '08F02', '4', '', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(1455, '4', 'Are authentication parameters under strict control?\r\nA strict control requires that the list of people able to change authentication rules, the credentials themselves and the surveillance rules of connection attempts be strictly limited, that there be a reinforced access control in order to be able to modify these rights and that any modification of these rights be logged and audited and that there be a general audit at least once a year of all authentication parameters.', 'QUESTION', '08F02-04', '08F02', '4', '2', '', 'R1', '', '', NULL),
	(1456, '5', 'Are the processes that guarantee authentication under strict control? \r\nA strict control requires that the software used has been validated and undergoes a regular test for integrity (seal) and that there is an audit at least once a year of the authentication procedures and processes.', 'QUESTION', '08F02-05', '08F02', '4', '3', '', 'R1', '', '', NULL),
	(1457, '6', 'Is there a regular audit of the privileged profiles effectively granted?', 'QUESTION', '08F02-06', '08F02', '4', '3', '', 'C1', '9.2.5', '11.2.4', NULL),
	(1458, '7', 'Is there a regular audit of the procedures of granting privileged rights and the security parameters attached to protecting profiles and rights?  ', 'QUESTION', '08F02-07', '08F02', '4', '3', '', 'C1', '', '', NULL),
	(1459, '3', 'Surveillance of system administrators` actions', 'CATEGORY', '08F03', '08F', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1460, '1', 'Has a detailed analysis been carried out of the events and operations carried out with administrative rights which may potentially have an impact on system security (configuration of security systems, access to sensitive information, usage of sensitive tools, download or modification of administrative tools etc.)?', 'QUESTION', '08F03-01', '08F03', '2', '', '', 'E2', '12.4.3', '10.10.4; 10.6.1', NULL),
	(1461, '2', 'Are these events recorded as well as all parameters which may be useful for their subsequent analysis? ', 'QUESTION', '08F03-02', '08F03', '4', '', '', 'E2', '12.4.3', '10.10.4; 10.6.1', NULL),
	(1462, '3', 'Is there a system able to detect any modification or deletion of a past record and to immediately trigger an alarm to a manager? ', 'QUESTION', '08F03-03', '08F03', '4', '2', '', 'E3', '12.4.3', '10.10.4', NULL),
	(1463, '4', 'Is there a summary of these records enabling management to detect abnormal behavior?', 'QUESTION', '08F03-04', '08F03', '4', '', '3', 'E3', '12.4.3', '10.10.4', NULL),
	(1464, '5', 'Is there a system enabling the detection of any modification of recording parameters and to immediately trigger an alarm to a manager? ', 'QUESTION', '08F03-05', '08F03', '4', '2', '', 'E3', '12.4.3', '10.10.4', NULL),
	(1465, '6', 'Does any inhibition of the recording and processing of the logged events system trigger an alarm to a manager? ', 'QUESTION', '08F03-06', '08F03', '4', '', '', 'E3', '12.4.3', '10.10.4', NULL),
	(1466, '7', 'Are all records or summary analyses protected against any falsification or destruction?', 'QUESTION', '08F03-07', '08F03', '2', '', '', 'E2', '12.4.3', '10.10.4', NULL),
	(1467, '8', 'Are all records or summary analyses kept for a long period?', 'QUESTION', '08F03-08', '08F03', '2', '', '', 'E2', '', '10.10.4', NULL),
	(1468, '9', 'Are the procedures, which record and process privileged operations, regularly audited? ', 'QUESTION', '08F03-09', '08F03', '2', '', '', 'C1', '', '10.10.4', NULL),
	(1469, '8', 'Audit and control Procedures relative to Information Systems', 'CATEGORY', '08G', '08', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1470, '1', 'Operation of Audit Control', 'CATEGORY', '08G01', '08G', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1471, '1', 'Have requirements and enforced procedures for the audit of IT systems been enacted by Management?', 'QUESTION', '08G01-01', '08G01', '4', '', '', 'E2', '12.7.1', '15.3.1', NULL),
	(1472, '2', 'Are the rules related to Information System audits, relevant procedures and associated responsibilities defined and documented?\r\nThe restrictions concern the type of access to data and applications, the authorized controls and processing, the deletion of sensitive data obtained, the flagging of certain operations, ... and the empowerment of the individuals conducting the audits. ', 'QUESTION', '08G01-02', '08G01', '3', '', '', 'E2', '12.7.1', '15.3.1', NULL),
	(1473, '3', 'Are the auditors independent of the concerned activities?', 'QUESTION', '08G01-03', '08G01', '2', '', '', 'E2', '12.7.1', '15.3.1', NULL),
	(1474, '4', 'Are audit operations conducted for critical data recorded?', 'QUESTION', '08G01-04', '08G01', '2', '', '', 'E3', '12.7.1', '15.3.1', NULL),
	(1475, '2', 'Protection of Tools and Audit Results', 'CATEGORY', '08G02', '08G', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1476, '1', 'Are the audit tools protected to avoid any unauthorized or malevolent use?\r\nThis applies particularly to intrusion testing and vulnerability assessments.', 'QUESTION', '08G02-01', '08G02', '3', '', '', 'E2', '', '15.3.2', NULL),
	(1477, '2', 'Are the audit results protected against any modification or disclosure?', 'QUESTION', '08G02-02', '08G02', '3', '', '', 'E2', '', '15.3.2', NULL),
	(1478, '3', 'Are the auditors` activities delimited?\r\nSuch a delimitation is especially recommended regarding external auditors', 'QUESTION', '08G02-03', '08G02', '2', '', '', 'E2', '', '15.3.2', NULL),
	(1479, '8', 'Management of IT related archives', 'CATEGORY', '08H', '08', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1480, '1', 'Organization of the management for IT archives', 'CATEGORY', '08H01', '08H', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1481, '1', 'Is there an organization in charge of archiving IT files that require to be kept over a long period? ', 'QUESTION', '08H01-01', '08H01', '4', '', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(1482, '2', 'Is there a procedure forcing users to use this archiving service for all the files that require to be kept over a long period? ', 'QUESTION', '08H01-02', '08H01', '4', '', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(1483, '3', 'Has a list of conditions been established and updated by each owner of data requiring to be archived concerning the archiving rules?', 'QUESTION', '08H01-03', '08H01', '4', '1', '', 'E1', '', '', NULL),
	(1484, '4', 'Are the requirements for external (legal and regulatory) and internal archiving defined and tackled by the entity owning the data and accepted by the top management at the highest level? \r\nThe consequences (legal, financial, image) of non compliance (partial or total) of the archiving requirements must be endorsed by the board of managers.', 'QUESTION', '08H01-04', '08H01', '4', '', '', 'E1', '16.1.7; 18.1.3', '13.2.3; 15.1.3', NULL),
	(1485, '5', 'Are service agreements negotiated with the IT department, considered as agents only for the data?\r\nEach agreement must state the requirements: content of the archives, retention duration, durability, capacity to trace, imputability, non disclosure, procedures and delay for disposal, administrative constraints, etc.\r\nA clear separation must be stated between the content of the archives, under responsibility of the owner of data, and the container (media, disks, tapes, cartridges) under the responsibility of the IT department.', 'QUESTION', '08H01-05', '08H01', '4', '1', '', 'E2', '18.1.3', '15.1.3', NULL),
	(1486, '6', 'Are the resources necessary for archiving the data known and financed over the longer term?', 'QUESTION', '08H01-06', '08H01', '2', '1', '', 'E2', '18.1.3', '15.1.3', NULL),
	(1487, '7', 'Are there regular readability tests of the archives?', 'QUESTION', '08H01-07', '08H01', '4', '', '', 'C1', '', '', NULL),
	(1488, '8', 'Are the possible modifications resulting from technological or regulatory evolutions, that may modify the content or the containers of the archives,  taken into account, documented and accepted by the management? \r\nThese evolutions cannot be avoided on the long term and all the external regulations must be respected in order to guarantee the conformity of the data to the original ones.', 'QUESTION', '08H01-08', '08H01', '4', '2', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(1489, '9', 'Is the existence of the hardware and software tools for the processing of the archives regularly controlled?', 'QUESTION', '08H01-09', '08H01', '2', '', '', 'C1', '', '', NULL),
	(1490, '10', 'Is there a regular control of the procedures stated for the archiving and any deviation related to the data owners? \r\nThe controls must also look for eliminating the possibilities of fraud involving the persons in charge of the operations as well as those who may have an access to the contents or the containers. ', 'QUESTION', '08H01-10', '08H01', '4', '2', '', 'C1', '', '', NULL),
	(1491, '11', 'Are all the procedures concerning the archiving policy audited regularly? ', 'QUESTION', '08H01-11', '08H01', '4', '3', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1492, '2', 'IT Archives access management', 'CATEGORY', '08H02', '08H', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1493, '1', 'Have the requirements and procedures to be followed to access the archives been specified by management? ', 'QUESTION', '08H02-01', '08H02', '2', '', '', 'E2', '', '15.3.1', NULL),
	(1494, '2', 'Does each archive or set of archives have a designated owner?', 'QUESTION', '08H02-02', '08H02', '4', '', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(1495, '3', 'Are requests for extracts from the archives accepted only from the designated owner? ', 'QUESTION', '08H02-03', '08H02', '4', '2', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(1496, '4', 'Is a request from the owner subject to authentication? ', 'QUESTION', '08H02-04', '08H02', '4', '2', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(1497, '5', 'Is this authentication check considered to be strong?', 'QUESTION', '08H02-05', '08H02', '4', '3', '', 'E3', '', '', NULL),
	(1498, '6', 'Given that users do not have access to the archives, does the archival department always keep the original version? ', 'QUESTION', '08H02-06', '08H02', '4', '3', '', 'E3', '', '', NULL),
	(1499, '7', 'Is access to the archives by archival personnel subject to strong authentication? ', 'QUESTION', '08H02-07', '08H02', '4', '3', '', 'E3', '', '', NULL),
	(1500, '8', 'Is each access recorded in a secure manner?', 'QUESTION', '08H02-08', '08H02', '4', '3', '', 'E3', '', '', NULL),
	(1501, '9', 'Is transfer of an archive or of a copy to the requester carried out in a secure manner? ', 'QUESTION', '08H02-09', '08H02', '4', '3', '', 'E3', '', '', NULL),
	(1502, '10', 'Are the conditions of access to the archives and the associated security systems audited regularly', 'QUESTION', '08H02-10', '08H02', '3', '2', '', 'C1', '', '', NULL),
	(1503, '3', 'Management of IT archive safety', 'CATEGORY', '08H03', '08H', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1504, '1', 'Are the archive storage locations equipped with suitable fire detection and extinction systems and water leakage detection and evacuation? ', 'QUESTION', '08H03-01', '08H03', '3', '2', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
