	(1618, '5', 'Do the procedures and mechanisms for storage, distribution and, more generally, management of keys offer a sufficient level of confidence and have they been approved by the Information Security Officer?\r\nThe possibility of having to recover these data on another hardware system or another version of the operating system needs to be anticipated.', 'QUESTION', '09C02-05', '09C02', '4', '3', '', 'E2', '10.1.2', '12.3.2', NULL),
