	(1700, '1', 'Securing application services on public networks\r\nInformation involved in application services passing over public networks should be protected from fraudulent activity, contract dispute and unauthorized disclosure and modification', 'CATEGORY', '09H01', '09H', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1701, '1', 'Is the migration of existing services from private to public networks organized with the associated parties ?\r\nAttention to the risk owners and all users should be prominent and the management requirements issues central to the decision', 'QUESTION', '09H01-01', '09H01', '2', '', '', '', '14.1.2', '', NULL),
	(1702, '2', 'Have the security requirements specific to making information available on public networks been analyzed and thus defined the necessary protections and assurance?', 'QUESTION', '09H01-02', '09H01', '2', '', '', 'E2', '14.1.1', '10.9.1', NULL),
	(1703, '3', 'Have the classification levels for the information and services assets received a special attention?\r\nThe value of Personally Identifiable Information and strategic elements for the organization should be carefully established (see worksheets T1 to T3)', 'QUESTION', '09H01-03', '09H01', '4', '2', '', '', '14.1.2', '', NULL),
	(1704, '4', 'Have Service level agreements for the permanence and continuity of the service been negotiated with the service providers ?\r\nThis is very important in the case of services obtained over the cloud and appropriate penalties should be clearly understood by the organization (e.g. in the case of interruption by the provider (error, accident, strike, bankruptcy, takeover, ...)) including the capacity to recover the proprietary data ', 'QUESTION', '09H01-04', '09H01', '3', '2', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1705, '5', 'Are the protection and verification of transactions appropriately managed?\r\nIncluding payment information provided by the customer, integrity, confidentiality, protection against replay, confirmation of receipt, non-repudiation, etc. to guard against fraud.', 'QUESTION', '09H01-05', '09H01', '3', '2', '', '', '14.1.2', '', NULL),
	(1706, '6', 'Are Service level agreements in place concerning the confidentiality of the information treated and/or stored by the service provider?\r\nMeans to control the agreements and to react rapidly should be guaranteed to the organization.', 'QUESTION', '09H01-06', '09H01', '3', '2', '', '', '14.1.1', '', NULL),
	(1707, '7', 'Have protections to the security risks associated to web access been integrated to the application?\r\nOWASP references 10 important threats like Injection flaws, cross site scripting and request forgery, broken sessions, insecure direct object references and cryptographic storage, security misconfiguration, failure to restrict URL access, insufficient transport layer protection, unvalidated redirects and forwards)', 'QUESTION', '09H01-07', '09H01', '4', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1708, '8', 'Have the likelihood of attacks and threats been specifically analyzed for the application services?\r\nCareful attention to  the level of the natural exposure settings in the worksheet Expo is required, firstly cyber attacks', 'QUESTION', '09H01-08', '09H01', '3', '', '', '', '14.1.2', '', NULL),
	(1709, '9', 'Are the authentication, control of rights and logging mechanisms specifically enforced for administrative operations?', 'QUESTION', '09H01-09', '09H01', '2', '2', '', '', '14.1.1', '', NULL),
	(1710, '10', 'Are the mutual levels of confidence (of each other`s identity, authorization, level of trust required in the integrity  and confidentiality of data exchanged) considered in regard of the requirements?\r\nThe quality of the security services 09A to 09G above should be appropriate with the requirements of the application service.', 'QUESTION', '09H01-10', '09H01', '3', '2', '', '', '14.1.2', '', NULL),
	(1711, '11', 'Is there a regular review, at least once a year, of the application services and corrective solutions envisaged?\r\nThis review shall also consider shadow applications and data on public networks', 'QUESTION', '09H01-11', '09H01', '2', '2', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1712, '2', 'Protecting application services transactions', 'CATEGORY', '09H02', '09H', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(1713, '1', 'Are specific security protection requirements defined and used for critical transactions attached to the application?\r\nCompliance with legal and regulatory requirements is imperative.', 'QUESTION', '09H02-01', '09H02', '3', '', '', '', '14.1.3', '', NULL),
	(1714, '2', 'Is the non disclosure of critical transactions protected by using strong cryptographic controls?\r\nSecret authentication information of all parties should be valid and verified, communication paths between them are encrypted, protocols used are secured, storage of the transaction details are located in a protected environment.', 'QUESTION', '09H02-02', '09H02', '3', '', '', '', '14.1.3', '', NULL),
