              "index": "3",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Has an activity recovery solution been defined and implemented to resolve each scenario identified above, in accordance with user requirements?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "2",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "17.1.2",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A17\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Information security aspects of business continuity management\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A17.1\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Information security continuity\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"17.1.2\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Implementing information security continuity\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": "14.1.3"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "11D07-04",\n              "index": "4",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Are the technical, organizational and human resources sufficient to address the organization`s requirements?\\r\\nThis means being able to correct personnel deficiencies",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "17.1.2",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A17\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Information security aspects of business continuity management\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A17.1\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Information security continuity\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"17.1.2\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Implementing information security continuity\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": "14.1.3"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n       