s required to obtain this guarantee are preferably full scale tests of each variant of scenario, involving all users. The results of the tests have to be registered and analyzed in order to improve the capability of the organization to answer to the situations considered. ",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "17.1.2; 17.1.3",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A17\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Information security aspects of business continuity management\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A17.1\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Information security continuity\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"17.1.2\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Implementing information security continuity\\"},{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A17\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Information security aspects of business continuity management\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A17.1\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Information security continuity\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"17.1.3\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Verify, review and evaluate information security continuity\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "3",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": "14.1.5"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "11D07-09",\n              "index": "9",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "If the recovery solutions include delivery of hardware components (which cannot be triggered during tests), is there a contractual commitment by the manufacturer or any relevant third party (distributor) to deliver the replacement hardware within fixed and anticipated time limits as stated in the recovery plan?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "ME