          "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "12E01-04",\n              "index": "4",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is the process of attributing special rights allocated only in relation to the profile of the holder?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "6.1.2",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A6\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Organization of information security\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A6.1\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Internal organization\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"6.1.2\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Segregation of duties\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "2",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": "10.1.3"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "12E01-05",\n              "index": "5",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is the process of granting (modification or revocation) of special rights to an individual strictly controlled?\\r\\nA strict control requires a formal recognition of the signature (electronic or not) of the requestor, that there be a tight control of access in order to attribute or modify such rights and that any modification of special rights be logged and audited.",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "3",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "9.2.3; 9.2.5",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A9\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Access control\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A9.2\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"User access management\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"9.2.3\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Management of privileged access rights\\"},{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A9\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Access control\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A9.2\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"User access management\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"9.2.5\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Review of user access rights\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "2",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": "11.2.2"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "12E01-06",\n              "index": "6",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is there a systematic process of removal of special rights at the time of departure of telecommunication operations staff?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "9.2.5",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A9\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Access control\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A9.2\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"User access management\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"9.2.5\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Review of user access rights\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": "11.2.4"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "12E01-07",\n              "index": "7",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is there a systematic process of removal of special rights at the time of role change of telecommunication operations staff?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "9.2.5",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A9\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Access control\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A9.2\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"User access management\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"9.2.5\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Review of user access rights\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": "11.2.4"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "12E01-08",\n              "index": "8",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is there a regular audit, at least once a year, of all special rights attributed?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "1",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "9.2.5",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A9\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Access control\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A9.2\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"User access management\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"9.2.5\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Review of user access rights\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "2",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": "11.2.4"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            }\n          ],\n          "gasf": [\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0231",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Enforce system access control policies",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "The system shall enforce the implementation of the [System Access Control Policy] to system appliances, objects, operation and data.",\n                "MEHARI_W": "3",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"824f2261-17da-436d-8a61-47b489684392\\":\\"INDAS0607F074.1_TN2_SRS\\",\\"d1896fa0-c90f-40a4-ad1b-7f28052048e5\\":\\"NIST-SP800-53_rev4\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"824f2261-17da-436d-8a61-47b489684392\\":\\"TCA_ACCESS_0010\\",\\"d1896fa0-c90f-40a4-ad1b-7f28052048e5\\":\\"AC-3\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "-"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0264",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Restrict security attributes modification",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "Modification of security attributes shall only be possible by specific, well-defined roles.",\n                "MEHARI_W": "3",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"b0f230da-0b0b-41b2-aac8-3ea2c049317f\\":\\"INDAS0607F074.1_TN2_SRS\\",\\"ce3c8f56-af3d-4daf-bdb2-8202eae3b95a\\":\\"INDAS0607F074.1_TN2_SRS\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"b0f230da-0b0b-41b2-aac8-3ea2c049317f\\":\\"TCA_SEC_MNGT_0020\\",\\"ce3c8f56-af3d-4daf-bdb2-8202eae3b95a\\":\\"TCA_SEC_MNGT_0010\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "Security attributes are all data that are used to configure the security features of the system."\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0258",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Prevent display of management-related functionalities to non-privileged users",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "The system shall prevent the presentation of information system management-related functionality at an interface for non-privileged users.",\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"04da66df-bda0-46bc-a96c-c81933d27273\\":\\"NIST-SP800-53_rev4\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"04da66df-bda0-46bc-a96c-c81933d27273\\":\\"SC-2(1)\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "This ensures that administration options (e.g., administrator privileges) are not available to general users (including prohibiting the use of the grey-out option commonly used to eliminate accessibility to such information). Such restrictions include, for example, not presenting administration options until users establish sessions with administrator privileges."\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            }\n          ],\n          "answers": {\n            "MEHARI_W": "",\n            "MEHARI_Min": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n            "MEHARI_Max": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n          },\n          "referenceObject": null,\n          "identifier": null,\n          "objType": "Audit",\n          "lockedBy": null\n        },\n        {\n          "category": "12E02",\n          "index": "2",\n          "type": "CATEGORY",\n          "value": "Authentication and control of the access rights of administrators and operational personnel ",\n          "children": [\n            {\n              "category": "12E02-01",\n              "index": "1",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is the authentication protocol used for administrators or holders of special rights considered to be secure?\\r\\nAn authentication protocol is considered secure if it is not susceptible to being broken by a listening device on the network or rendered inoperable by specialists tools (in particular password crack tools ). Such security usually uses cryptographic methods.",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "4",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "6.1.2",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A6\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Organization of information security\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A6.1\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Internal organization\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"6.1.2\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Segregation of duties\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "12E02-02",\n              "index": "2",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Are the rules, for instance in the case of passwords, considered to be very strict?\\r\\nStrict rules impose the use of tested non-trivial passwords, using a mixture of different types of characters and of a reasonable length (ten characters). It is desirable that these rules have been approved by the Information Security Officer",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "6.1.2",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A6\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Organization of information security\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A6.1\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Internal organization\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"6.1.2\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Segregation of duties\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "12E02-03",\n              "index": "3",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is there a consistent control of the administrator`s rights, of its context, and of the suitability of this context with the requested access, as per formal rules of access control?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "6.1.2",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A6\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Organization of information security\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A6.1\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Internal organization\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"6.1.2\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Segregation of duties\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "12E02-04",\n              "index": "4",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Are authentication parameters under strict control?\\r\\nA strict control requires that the list of people able to change authentication rules, the credentials themselves and the surveillance rules of connection attempts be strictly limited, that there be a reinforced access control in order to be able to modify these rights and that any modification of these rights be logged and audited and that there be a general audit at least once a year of all authentication parameters.",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "6.1.2",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A6\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Organization of information security\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A6.1\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Internal organization\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"6.1.2\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Segregation of duties\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "2",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "12E02-05",\n              "index": "5",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Are the processes that guarantee authentication under strict control?\\r\\nA strict control requires that the software used has been validated and undergoes a regular test for integrity (seal) and that there is an audit at least once a year of the authentication procedures and processes.",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "3",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "12E02-06",\n              "index": "6",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is there a regular audit of the security parameters attached to protecting profiles and rights?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "3",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            }\n          ],\n          "gasf": [],\n          "answers": {\n            "MEHARI_W": "",\n            "MEHARI_Min": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n            "MEHARI_Max": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n          },\n          "referenceObject": null,\n          "identifier": null,\n          "objType": "Audit",\n          "lockedBy": null\n        },\n        {\n          "category": "12E03",\n          "index": "3",\n          "type": "CATEGORY",\n          "value": "Surveillance of system administrators` actions over the equipment and systems",\n          "children": [\n            {\n              "category": "12E03-01",\n              "index": "1",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Has a detailed analysis been carried out of the events and operations carried out with administrative rights which may potentially have an impact on system security (configuration of security systems, access to sensitive information, usage of sensitive tools, download or modification of administrative tools etc.)?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "12.4.3",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[{\\"ClauseId\\":\\"A12\\",\\"Clause\\":\\"Operations security\\",\\"ObjectiveId\\":\\"A12.4\\",\\"Objective\\":\\"Logging and monitoring\\",\\"ControlId\\":\\"12.4.3\\",\\"Control\\":\\"Administrator and operator logs\\"}]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": "10.10.4"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "12E03-02",\n              "index": "2",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Are these events recorded as well as all parameters which may be useful for their subsequent analysis? ",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers":