	(2160, '3', 'Utilization of cryptographic equipment', 'CATEGORY', '12D03', '12D', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2161, '1', 'Are encryption of exchanges mechanisms settable in accordance to the non-disclosure requirements established?', 'QUESTION', '12D03-01', '12D03', '4', '', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(2162, '2', 'Are the encryption capabilities explained to all the staff? ', 'QUESTION', '12D03-02', '12D03', '4', '', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(2163, '3', 'Have the user functions requiring a protection of the telecommunication exchanges been analyzed?', 'QUESTION', '12D03-03', '12D03', '4', '3', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(2164, '4', 'Have encryption functions been installed on all the corresponding user equipment? ', 'QUESTION', '12D03-04', '12D03', '4', '3', '', 'E2', '', '', NULL),
	(2165, '12', ' Control of administrative rights', 'CATEGORY', '12E', '12', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2166, '1', 'Management of privileged access rights granted on equipment and systems  (administrative rights) ', 'CATEGORY', '12E01', '12E', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2167, '1', 'Have profiles been defined, within telecommunication operations staff, corresponding to each type of activity (system administration, administration of security equipment, system monitoring, management of data storage and backup functions etc.)?', 'QUESTION', '12E01-01', '12E01', '1', '', '', 'E1', '6.1.2; 9.2.3; 9.2.5', '10.1.3; 11.2.2', NULL),
	(2168, '2', 'For each profile have the necessary rights and privileges been defined? ', 'QUESTION', '12E01-02', '12E01', '4', '2', '', 'E1', '6.1.2', '10.1.3', NULL),
	(2169, '3', 'Does the process of attributing special rights require the formal authorization of management (or the manager responsible for external service providers) at a sufficiently high level?', 'QUESTION', '12E01-03', '12E01', '4', '2', '', 'E2', '6.1.2', '10.1.3', NULL),
	(2170, '4', 'Is the process of attributing special rights allocated only in relation to the profile of the holder?', 'QUESTION', '12E01-04', '12E01', '4', '2', '', 'E2', '6.1.2', '10.1.3', NULL),
	(2171, '5', 'Is the process of granting (modification or revocation) of special rights to an individual strictly controlled?\r\nA strict control requires a formal recognition of the signature (electronic or not) of the requestor, that there be a tight control of access in order to attribute or modify such rights and that any modification of special rights be logged and audited.', 'QUESTION', '12E01-05', '12E01', '4', '2', '3', 'R1', '9.2.3; 9.2.5', '11.2.2', NULL),
	(2172, '6', 'Is there a systematic process of removal of special rights at the time of departure of telecommunication operations staff?', 'QUESTION', '12E01-06', '12E01', '2', '', '', 'E2', '9.2.5', '11.2.4', NULL),
	(2173, '7', 'Is there a systematic process of removal of special rights at the time of role change of telecommunication operations staff?', 'QUESTION', '12E01-07', '12E01', '2', '', '', 'E2', '9.2.5', '11.2.4', NULL),
	(2174, '8', 'Is there a regular audit, at least once a year, of all special rights attributed?', 'QUESTION', '12E01-08', '12E01', '1', '2', '', 'C1', '9.2.5', '11.2.4', NULL),
	(2175, '2', 'Authentication and control of the access rights of administrators and operational personnel ', 'CATEGORY', '12E02', '12E', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2176, '1', 'Is the authentication protocol used for administrators or holders of special rights considered to be secure?\r\nAn authentication protocol is considered secure if it is not susceptible to being broken by a listening device on the network or rendered inoperable by specialists tools (in particular password crack tools ). Such security usually uses cryptographic methods.', 'QUESTION', '12E02-01', '12E02', '4', '', '4', 'E2', '6.1.2', '', NULL),
	(2177, '2', 'Are the rules, for instance in the case of passwords, considered to be very strict?\r\nStrict rules impose the use of tested non-trivial passwords, using a mixture of different types of characters and of a reasonable length (ten characters). It is desirable that these rules have been approved by the Information Security Officer', 'QUESTION', '12E02-02', '12E02', '2', '', '', 'E2', '6.1.2', '', NULL),
	(2178, '3', 'Is there a consistent control of the administrator`s rights, of its context, and of the suitability of this context with the requested access, as per formal rules of access control?', 'QUESTION', '12E02-03', '12E02', '4', '', '', 'E2', '6.1.2', '', NULL),
	(2179, '4', 'Are authentication parameters under strict control?\r\nA strict control requires that the list of people able to change authentication rules, the credentials themselves and the surveillance rules of connection attempts be strictly limited, that there be a reinforced access control in order to be able to modify these rights and that any modification of these rights be logged and audited and that there be a general audit at least once a year of all authentication parameters.', 'QUESTION', '12E02-04', '12E02', '4', '2', '', 'R1', '6.1.2', '', NULL),
	(2180, '5', 'Are the processes that guarantee authentication under strict control?\r\nA strict control requires that the software used has been validated and undergoes a regular test for integrity (seal) and that there is an audit at least once a year of the authentication procedures and processes.', 'QUESTION', '12E02-05', '12E02', '4', '3', '', 'R1', '', '', NULL),
	(2181, '6', 'Is there a regular audit of the security parameters attached to protecting profiles and rights?', 'QUESTION', '12E02-06', '12E02', '4', '3', '', 'C1', '', '', NULL),
	(2182, '3', 'Surveillance of system administrators` actions over the equipment and systems', 'CATEGORY', '12E03', '12E', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2183, '1', 'Has a detailed analysis been carried out of the events and operations carried out with administrative rights which may potentially have an impact on system security (configuration of security systems, access to sensitive information, usage of sensitive tools, download or modification of administrative tools etc.)?', 'QUESTION', '12E03-01', '12E03', '2', '', '', 'E2', '12.4.3', '10.10.4', NULL),
	(2184, '2', 'Are these events recorded as well as all parameters which may be useful for their subsequent analysis? ', 'QUESTION', '12E03-02', '12E03', '4', '', '', 'E2', '12.4.3', '10.10.4', NULL),
	(2185, '3', 'Is there a system able to detect any modification or deletion of a past record and to immediately trigger an alarm to a manager? ', 'QUESTION', '12E03-03', '12E03', '4', '2', '', 'E3', '12.4.3', '10.10.4', NULL),
	(2186, '4', 'Is there a summary of these records enabling management to detect abnormal behavior?', 'QUESTION', '12E03-04', '12E03', '4', '', '3', 'E3', '12.4.3', '10.10.4', NULL),
	(2187, '5', 'Is there a system enabling the detection of any modification of recording parameters and to immediately trigger an alarm to a manager? ', 'QUESTION', '12E03-05', '12E03', '4', '2', '', 'E3', '12.4.3', '10.10.4', NULL),
	(2188, '6', 'Does any inhibition of the recording and processing of the logged events system trigger an alarm to a manager? ', 'QUESTION', '12E03-06', '12E03', '4', '', '', 'E3', '12.4.3', '10.10.4', NULL),
	(2189, '7', 'Are all records or summary analyses protected against any falsification or destruction?', 'QUESTION', '12E03-07', '12E03', '2', '', '', 'E2', '12.4.3', '10.10.4', NULL),
