ASF_0033",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Document relevant logs",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "All relevant logs that need to be analysed for the system shall be described on the CIG.",\n                "MEHARI_W": "3",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"73c9985c-dcfe-4fb3-b52a-22b7bdc92cc6\\":\\"ESA\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"73c9985c-dcfe-4fb3-b52a-22b7bdc92cc6\\":\\"GASF\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "-"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0041",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Define assumptions on system environment",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "The assumptions on system environment shall be aligned to the CIG.",\n                "MEHARI_W": "3",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"52ffdf1f-b216-4b44-963c-42ef3dcb8a33\\":\\"ESA\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"52ffdf1f-b216-4b44-963c-42ef3dcb8a33\\":\\"GASF\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "E.g. deployment environment (physical and logical location), network, user access, ..."\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0036",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Specification of information system connnection",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "For each external and internal interface, the interface characteristics, security requirements, and nature of the information communicated shall be documented in an ICD.",\n                "MEHARI_W": "3",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"7fe2e656-4f67-489e-a68d-50fbc374b012\\":\\"NIST-SP800-53_rev4\\",\\"94399d14-f9f6-4bbf-a113-018f193d6e38\\":\\"NIST-SP800-53_rev4\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"7fe2e656-4f67-489e-a68d-50fbc374b012\\":\\"CA-9\\",\\"94399d14-f9f6-4bbf-a113-018f193d6e38\\":\\"CA-3\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "This applies to dedicated connections between information systems and between organizational information systems and (separate) constituent system components (i.e., intra-system connections) including, for example, system connections with mobile devices, printers, copiers, facsimile machines, scanners, and sensors."\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0042",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Document the third party software licensing",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "The contractor shall document in the CIG the third party software used by the software system and clearly stating the type, if commercial or open source. For each open source software the type of license shall be specified and included on the delivery CD.",\n                "MEHARI_W": "3",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"04128b66-cc06-41c3-84f5-d93b63dc329f\\":\\"ESA\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"04128b66-cc06-41c3-84f5-d93b63dc329f\\":\\"GASF\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "This includes COTS (Commercial Of The Shelf) and any other third party software not developed under supervision or approval of ESA.\\nThe delivery CD contains a licence overview file containing all types of licence used and their associated licence file."\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0028",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Define access hardening steps",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "The contractor shall document the specific hardening steps taken to restrict access to the target system/software.",\n                "MEHARI_W": "3",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"4bbd48da-c47a-4ba2-8f7b-583ee47663ef\\":\\"ESA\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"4bbd48da-c47a-4ba2-8f7b-583ee47663ef\\":\\"GASF\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "-"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0035",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Group and restrict access to particular service files",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "All executable, libraries, configuration files, tools of a particular service shall be grouped (if possible) and stored in directories owned by the appropriate role. Modification/write access rights shall be denied for all other users.\\nThis shall be documented in the CIG.",\n                "MEHARI_W": "3",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"761becb1-31a7-4e97-8064-b86632c116bf\\":\\"INDAS0607F074.1_TN2_SRS\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"761becb1-31a7-4e97-8064-b86632c116bf\\":\\"TCA_OS_BIOS_0110\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "This requirement applies to the files dedicated to the applications (services)."\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0030",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Delete inactive accounts",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "The contractor shall include the deletion of inactive accounts in the user account management documentation in the [host document].",\n                "MEHARI_W": "3",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"de51f0bb-ad01-47e3-b8a7-a5cd3a22ffd6\\":\\"INDAS0607F074.1_TN2_SRS\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"de51f0bb-ad01-47e3-b8a7-a5cd3a22ffd6\\":\\"TCA_IDENT_0020\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "The old and inactive accounts should be deleted.\\nThis prevents illicit use of accounts by other users."\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0034",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Change default password after installation",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "The contractor shall include the modification of the default password after software installation in the user account management documentation in the [host document].",\n                "MEHARI_W": "3",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"8f775318-964f-4c92-a165-bb41f7ffcfbc\\":\\"INDAS0607F074.1_TN2_SRS\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"8f775318-964f-4c92-a165-bb41f7ffcfbc\\":\\"TCA_IDENT_AUTH_0180\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0040",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Define information flows",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "The information flows shall be documented in the ICD.",\n                "MEHARI_W": "3",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"64ae069e-4707-4ca6-b49c-cdd14b391907\\":\\"ESA\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"64ae069e-4707-4ca6-b49c-cdd14b391907\\":\\"GASF\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "E.g. ports used."\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0031",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Disable default accounts",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "The contractor shall include the deactivation of default accounts in the user account management documentation in the [host document].",\n                "MEHARI_W": "3",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"2026547a-1547-4627-9ad2-214bd95d4179\\":\\"INDAS0607F074.1_TN2_SRS\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"2026547a-1547-4627-9ad2-214bd95d4179\\":\\"TCA_IDENT_0030\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "Default or standard accounts / account names (e.g. Guest) shall be disabled.\\nThese accounts are an easy target even for not-too-experienced attackers."\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "GASF_0037",\n              "index": "01",\n              "type": "GASF",\n              "value": "Provide checksum",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "Description": "The Software Release Notes (SRN) shall contain or describe the location of checksums for the application\'s files.",\n                "MEHARI_W": "3",\n                "MEHARI_R_V5": "{\\"2009\\":{\\"3fabb0b2-8e9f-4cc8-be0a-b90ac3af4c0c\\":\\"ESA\\"},\\"2010\\":{\\"3fabb0b2-8e9f-4cc8-be0a-b90ac3af4c0c\\":\\"GASF\\"}}",\n                "MEHARI_R_V4": "Checksums permit to check the integrity of the files and should therefore be provided. Integrity checks shall rely on cryptographic Message Authentication Code (MAC)"\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            }\n          ],\n          "answers": {\n            "MEHARI_W": "",\n            "MEHARI_Min": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n            "MEHARI_Max": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n          },\n          "referenceObject": null,\n          "identifier": null,\n          "objType": "Audit",\n          "lockedBy": null\n        },\n        {\n          "category": "14E03",\n          "index": "3",\n          "type": "CATEGORY",\n          "value": "Updates",\n          "children": [\n            {\n              "category": "14E03-01",\n              "index": "1",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Are the people authorized to update the documents clearly identified?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "14E03-02",\n              "index": "2",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is it clearly stated that all updates must be approved?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            }\n          ],\n          "gasf": [],\n          "answers": {\n            "MEHARI_W": "",\n            "MEHARI_Min": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n            "MEHARI_Max": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n          },\n          "referenceObject": null,\n          "identifier": null,\n          "objType": "Audit",\n          "lockedBy": null\n        },\n        {\n          "category": "14E04",\n          "index": "4",\n          "type": "CATEGORY",\n          "value": "Document naming and versioning management",\n          "children": [\n            {\n              "category": "14E04-01",\n              "index": "1",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is there a consistent numbering scheme for the documents that takes into account various versions? ",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "14E04-02",\n              "index": "2",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Are all modifications summarized in a document history section?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            }\n          ],\n          "gasf": [],\n          "answers": {\n            "MEHARI_W": "",\n            "MEHARI_Min": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n            "MEHARI_Max": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n          },\n          "referenceObject": null,\n          "identifier": null,\n          "objType": "Audit",\n          "lockedBy": null\n        },\n        {\n          "category": "14E05",\n          "index": "5",\n          "type": "CATEGORY",\n          "value": "Documentation disposal",\n          "children": [\n            {\n              "category": "14E05-01",\n              "index": "1",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is there a document classification scheme that defines the level of access rights for different users?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "4",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "2",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "14E05-02",\n              "index": "2",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is there a mechanism in place  for publishing information according to the users` access rights? ",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            }\n          ],\n          "gasf": [],\n          "answers": {\n            "MEHARI_W": "",\n            "MEHARI_Min": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n            "MEHARI_Max": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n          },\n          "referenceObject": null,\n          "identifier": null,\n          "objType": "Audit",\n          "lockedBy": null\n        },\n        {\n          "category": "14E06",\n          "index": "6",\n          "type": "CATEGORY",\n          "value": "Withdrawing of obsolete documents",\n          "children": [\n            {\n              "category": "14E06-01",\n              "index": "1",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is the procedure for withdrawing obsolete documents described?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            },\n            {\n              "category": "14E06-02",\n              "index": "2",\n              "type": "QUESTION",\n              "value": "Is the implementation of this procedure regularly checked by the responsible managers?",\n              "children": [],\n              "gasf": [],\n              "answers": {\n                "MEHARI_W": "2",\n                "MEHARI_Min": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n                "MEHARI_Max": "",\n                "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n              },\n              "referenceObject": null,\n              "identifier": null,\n              "objType": "Audit",\n              "lockedBy": null\n            }\n          ],\n          "gasf": [],\n          "answers": {\n            "MEHARI_W": "",\n            "MEHARI_Min": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n            "MEHARI_Max": "",\n            "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n          },\n          "referenceObject": null,\n          "identifier": null,\n          "objType": "Audit",\n          "lockedBy": null\n        }\n      ],\n      "gasf": [],\n      "answers": {\n        "MEHARI_W": "",\n        "MEHARI_Min": "",\n        "MEHARI_ISO13": "",\n        "MEHARI_ISO13_info": "[]",\n        "MEHARI_Max": "",\n        "MEHARI_ISO5": ""\n      },\n      "referenceObject": null,\n      "identifier": null,\n      "objType": "Audit",\n      "lockedBy": null\n    }\n  ],\n  "identifier": null,\n  "objType": "Audit",\n  "lockedBy": null\n}'),
	(2407, '14', 'Establish the management system', 'CATEGORY', '14A', '14', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2408, '1', 'Define the boundaries of the ISMS ', 'CATEGORY', '14A01', '14A', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2409, '1', 'Are the boundaries and scope of the ISMS resulting from a preliminary study of the expectations of the top management and the stakeholders? ', 'QUESTION', '14A01-01', '14A01', '4', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2410, '2', 'Do the boundaries contain the processes and assets of vital value for the organization? \r\nThey should specify the sites, organizational units and business activities as well as external interfaces.  \r\nAny exclusions from the scope must be documented and justified.  ', 'QUESTION', '14A01-02', '14A01', '2', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2411, '2', 'Define the ISMS policy', 'CATEGORY', '14A02', '14A', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2412, '1', 'Does the ISMS policy result from a preliminary study of the expectations of the stakeholders? ', 'QUESTION', '14A02-01', '14A02', '4', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2413, '2', 'Does this policy state clearly and precisely the commitments of the management relative to information security?', 'QUESTION', '14A02-02', '14A02', '1', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2414, '3', 'Does this policy take into account the requirements of the organization towards criteria such as Availability, Integrity and non disclosure? ', 'QUESTION', '14A02-03', '14A02', '2', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2415, '4', 'Does this policy  take into account legal and regulatory requirements?', 'QUESTION', '14A02-04', '14A02', '2', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2416, '5', 'Does this policy take into account the commitment to use precise evaluation of risks?', 'QUESTION', '14A02-05', '14A02', '2', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2417, '6', 'Have clear risk reduction and management objectives been established?', 'QUESTION', '14A02-06', '14A02', '4', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2418, '7', 'Has this policy been approved by the top management of the organization?', 'QUESTION', '14A02-07', '14A02', '2', '2', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2419, '8', 'Has the management of the organization reserved the necessary resources and funding over the long term? ', 'QUESTION', '14A02-08', '14A02', '1', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2420, '3', 'Define the risk assessment approach and associated metrics', 'CATEGORY', '14A03', '14A', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2421, '1', 'Has a  risk assessment method that fits to the requirements of the organization been selected? ', 'QUESTION', '14A03-01', '14A03', '4', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2422, '2', 'Does the method permit to analyze the information security requirements for each asset in accordance to the business, laws and  regulations?', 'QUESTION', '14A03-02', '14A03', '2', '2', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2423, '3', 'Does the method permit to classify the feared dysfunctions on a scale applicable to the entire organization? ', 'QUESTION', '14A03-03', '14A03', '1', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2424, '4', 'Does the method provide precise metrics allowing a rational and reproducible risk assessment?\r\nThe seriousness of each risk being classified within a previously defined scale.', 'QUESTION', '14A03-04', '14A03', '1', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2425, '4', 'Identification of the risks', 'CATEGORY', '14A04', '14A', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2426, '1', 'Does this risk analysis method used allow to identify the supporting assets attached to  each operational process and to each primary asset?', 'QUESTION', '14A04-01', '14A04', '4', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2427, '2', 'Does the method permit to identify the threats and their consequences relative to the security objectives ( e.g. Availability, integrity, Confidentiality)?', 'QUESTION', '14A04-02', '14A04', '4', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2428, '3', 'Does the method permit to identify, in a precise way, the vulnerabilities according to the security measures in place?', 'QUESTION', '14A04-03', '14A04', '2', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2429, '4', 'Does the method permit to describe finely the scenarios that may exploit the threats and vulnerabilities? ', 'QUESTION', '14A04-04', '14A04', '2', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2430, '5', 'Does the method permit to identify the impacts on the activity for each scenario (through a precise criteria and asset)? ', 'QUESTION', '14A04-05', '14A04', '4', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2431, '6', 'Does the method permit to identify the links between each asset and the owners of data and processes?', 'QUESTION', '14A04-06', '14A04', '2', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2432, '5', 'Analysis and evaluation of the risks', 'CATEGORY', '14A05', '14A', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2433, '1', 'Does the risk analysis method permit to assess the levels of risk reduction resulting from the security measures in place or planned?', 'QUESTION', '14A05-01', '14A05', '2', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2434, '2', 'Does the method provide the elements allowing to assess the likelihood of each risk scenario? ', 'QUESTION', '14A05-02', '14A05', '4', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2435, '3', 'Does the method permit to reduce the likelihood of the scenarios resulting from the current (and planned) security measures (or controls)? ', 'QUESTION', '14A05-03', '14A05', '2', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2436, '4', 'Is it possible to adapt the likelihood levels resulting from changes in the organization?', 'QUESTION', '14A05-04', '14A05', '2', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2437, '5', 'Is the risk seriousness level clearly related to the impact and likelihood  values for each scenario ?', 'QUESTION', '14A05-05', '14A05', '1', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2438, '6', 'Does the method provide the elements allowing to classify the seriousness level for each risk scenario? \r\nHis level should be used to determine whether each risk is acceptable or require further treatment', 'QUESTION', '14A05-06', '14A05', '4', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2439, '6', 'Selection of risk treatment options', 'CATEGORY', '14A06', '14A', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2440, '1', 'Does the method permit to figure out the risk treatment options appropriate for the organization ? \r\nBased on the possible options (Accept, Avoid, Transfer or Reduce lye risk) and the criteria of acceptance already established.', 'QUESTION', '14A06-01', '14A06', '2', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2441, '2', 'Does the method permit to analyze the risk acceptance criteria for each scenario?', 'QUESTION', '14A06-02', '14A06', '2', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
	(2442, '7', 'Selection of the measures (controls) for risk reduction', 'CATEGORY', '14A07', '14A', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL),
